a full 9 months later and our baby is finally here 😂 @guess Seductive Blue 2023 global fragrance campaign shot by @joshryanphotos 

Seeing the perfect, polished, finished results is always fun but let me tell you, the process is the best part. As cliche as that sounds, it’s true. Shooting in another country with different elements, weather and resources forever bonds you to your crew - kind of like sleepaway camp lol. You have to use a different type of creativity and learn to be adaptable to be able to get your job done even if you’re in one boat and the talent is in another (holding the boats together with my foot while @erinmichellexo holds my brushes).

I’m beyond blessed to get to travel the world for my job with the best people. I’m not sure how the perfume smells but I can tell you the footage came out 🔥🔥🔥

A few weeks ago 🍷 with my girl @neenaroe 
.
.
